org.echo.mobile.framework.model

Class Authority.Deserializer

  • org.echo.mobile.framework.model.Authority.Deserializer
  • Enclosing class:
    Authority

    public static class Authority.Deserializer

    Custom deserializer used while parsing the 'get_account' API call response.

    This will deserialize an account authority in the form:

    { "weight_threshold": 1, "account_auths": [], "key_auths": [BTS6yoiaoC4p23n31AV4GnMy5QDh5yUQEUmU4PmNxRQPGg7jjPkBq,1], "address_auths": [] }

    See Also:
